paraphrases: Which courses are the least difficult ?
Which classes are the least difficult ?
What are the easiest courses for me to take ?
sql: SELECT DISTINCT COURSEalias0.DEPARTMENT , COURSEalias0.NUMBER , PROGRAM_COURSEalias0.WORKLOAD FROM COURSE AS COURSEalias0 INNER JOIN PROGRAM_COURSE AS PROGRAM_COURSEalias0 WHERE PROGRAM_COURSEalias0.WORKLOAD IS NOT NULL ORDER BY PROGRAM_COURSEalias0.WORKLOAD LIMIT 10 ;
